name: Itty Bitty Red Aztec Headband
description:
D E S C R I P T I O N:

This Red Leather Bow Aztec Headband is perfect with any outfit and is possibly my fav little hair accessory! 

Note: The grain and distressed look In every bow is different and unique. No 2 Bows are alike! 

--------------------------------

D E T A I L S: 
- Each Bow is securly attached to Aztec Headband. 
Note: Felt is used on the backside so no irritation occurs.
- Bows Measure 2.5 in from tip to tip

--------------------------------

Typically ships within 3-5 business days. If you need it sooner, please let me know and I would happy to work with you.

-----------------------------------

S I Z E S: 

Please specify size during checkout. If you don't, size 0-3 mos will be sent by default:

Newborn: 12.5-13 in
0-3mos: 14 inches
3-6mos: 15 inches
6mos-12mos: 16 inches
1yr-3yrs: 17 inches
3yrs-Adult: 18 inches
